long_description: Step into a new breed of fitness shoe with the New Balance 1765 Walking Shoes for women. These fitness walkers offer you a premium ride that's a combination of style and comfort. FantomFit is a skeletally engineered upper that provides ultralight support and fit; it is created by fusing 2 extremely thin materials with a no-sew process. Synthetic mesh upper with synthetic overlays breathes well to keep your feet dry. Innovative REVlite midsole provides premium responsiveness and durability at a 30% lighter weight than other foams with comparable performance. N2 low-to-the-ground cushioning technology is a responsive, durable, sustainable cushioning system in a low profile execution. Medial Post consists of higher-density compression-molded EVA, located on inside edge of shoe, to help prevent over-pronation. Lightweight rubber outsoles provide good traction.
